    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏玩家群：120067130 </h2>《我要写小说》是一款养成类模拟经营游戏，玩家要从一名一穷二白的网文写手开始，一步一步提升自己的写作能力，不断汲取灵感，磨炼笔力，最终成为一名人尽皆知的著名作家。<br><br><br>游戏重制版本，现已上线！为大家带来诸多全新玩法。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >重走小说发展之路</h2>穿越！体验中国小说行业发展历程，重新经历各个年代，从出版社到线上网站，感受写手在时代浪潮下如何辛勤耕耘，拼搏不息。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819980/extras/dcf66e1a373ad247469384dcdc11e9a7.poster.avif?t=1755111621\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819980/extras/dcf66e1a373ad247469384dcdc11e9a7.webm?t=1755111621\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819980/extras/dcf66e1a373ad247469384dcdc11e9a7.mp4?t=1755111621\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >提升写作能力</h2>在不断写作的过程中，玩家的能力也将得到提升，当然你也可以通过学习来提升能力。不断解锁更多的写作题材，能否找到最适合自己的写作套路将完全由玩家自己来决定！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819980/extras/e3b642711a32561f0e0834824fdf9a10.poster.avif?t=1755111621\" width=600 height=466 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819980/extras/e3b642711a32561f0e0834824fdf9a10.webm?t=1755111621\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819980/extras/e3b642711a32561f0e0834824fdf9a10.mp4?t=1755111621\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >创造提炼角色</h2>通过构思来获得各种各样的角色，不同的角色拥有不同的属性和技能，甚至是连携技。选择适合的角色成为你小说的主角、配角，他们会协助你完成创作，让整个过程更具代入感。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819980/extras/83289918f8cf4f55423dcd28a893fccf.poster.avif?t=1755111621\" width=600 height=502 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819980/extras/83289918f8cf4f55423dcd28a893fccf.webm?t=1755111621\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819980/extras/83289918f8cf4f55423dcd28a893fccf.mp4?t=1755111621\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >敏锐洞察市场</h2>整个市场的书站，出版社会根据时间的推移增加或者减少客户群的大小，同时也会因为一些大事件发生网站升级，降级，甚至网站关闭，出现新网站等现象。你需要随机应变，确定市场倾向写出受更多读着喜爱的作品。<br><br><br>努力去成为一名叱咤小说行业的顶级写手吧！更多特色内容玩法，还请进入游戏体验。",
